1:05:20.317 --> 1:05:22.150
I'll call you tomorrow, okay?

1:05:22.152 --> 1:05:22.984
Okay cool.

1:05:22.986 --> 1:05:23.885
Love you.

1:05:30.861 --> 1:05:33.428
